  "description": "A rainfall product based only on the application of SM2RAIN algorithm to ASCAT soil moisture observations is under development in the framework of H SAF project. The rainfall dataset covers the period 2007-2022 taking advantages of the long record of ASCAT retrieval. The product is available on a global scale at daily temporal resolution over a regular grid of 10 km. The product has been release up to December 2022.",
